data.description: Welcome to this updated home with attached 1 car garage and long driveway to fit multiple cars. This charming single family house features a spacious living room adorned with original wood flooring and beautiful porcelain wood burning fireplace. The open-concept  kitchen and dining room are seamlessly connected by a stylish porcelain island. An extra room that can be used for storage/office/den. A sun porch for cool evenings and sunny days to relax leading to the backyard. On the second floor you will find 3 nice sized bedrooms with closets and full bathroom with tub and Bluetooth shower speaker. This home comes  with finished basement with a large family room or extra bedroom with lots of closets. A laundry room located in the basement  with newer wash and dryer. Backyard comes furnished with a new gazebo, seating, dinning table, and a new patio.
